subject: College Athletics
Fiesta Bowl
Football (College)
lead_paragraph: Nine of the 11 members of an N.C.A.A. panel that will help decide the Fiesta Bowl’s fate attended a bowl-sponsored retreat that included free meals, resort rooms and golf outings.
